os explosivos de guerra</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/pt/acoes/violencia-sexual" title="">Violência sexual</a></li><li class="leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/pt/acoes/visita-detidos" title="">Visita a detidos</a></li><li class="last leaf"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/pt/ebola-vitimas-estigma-e-medo" title="">Ebola</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class="visible-sm visible-xs list-languages"> <select class="styled-language-select i-arrow-down-after redirection-select"><option value="https://www.icrc.org/pt/guerra-e-o-direito/desafios-contemporaneos-do-dih" selected="selected">PT</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl">EN</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/fr/guerre-et-droit/defis-contemporains-pour-le-dih">FR</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/es/guerra-y-derecho/desafios-contemporaneos-del-dih">ES</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/zh/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl">ZH</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/ar/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl">AR</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/ru/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl">RU</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/de/krieg-recht/aktuelle-debatten-zum-hvr">DE</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/it">IT</option><option value="https://www.icrc.org/en/languages">Outros</option> </select></div></div></div></div> </header></div> <nav class="navbar navbar--main clearfix js_navbar" id="main-menu" role="navigation"><div class="container"><div class="nav-sub"> <button type="button" class="nav-toggle i-menu pull-left js_toggle" data-target=".navbar--main"> <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span> </button><div class="pull-right"><div class="nav-donate nav-link-main-container visible-sm visible-xs"> <a href="https://doe.cicv.org.br/institucional/?utm_source=institucional&utm_medium=site-cicv&utm_campaign=institucional-DM" class="bg-red nav-link-main">F